ibutions of the two proton\nconfigurations depend on how the sample is hydrated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Apr 2014 19:44:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Jul 2015 20:12:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-28"}
