of convergence, final solution cost, and ability to find difficult\npassages while demonstrating less dependence on the state dimension and range\nof the planning problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Apr 2014 23:44:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Jun 2014 12:30:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 28 Nov 2014 14:31:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-01"}
